The CCST IT Support certification validates the essential knowledge and skills necessary to demonstrate work-ready technical support requirements. This certification is for candidates looking to work as technical support in various roles, such as help desk support technician. The successful candidates are qualified to enter the workforce as support specialists, support technicians, support auditors, and analysts<br/><img src='/images/CCST IT.png' width='500' height='500'>
